{"tid":1153300,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"川普建議 對中國的進口商品徵收45%的關稅","createTime":"2019-05-13T13:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T15:35:07.000Z","uid":13663,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"846264bedb7a5443cc8d2cfb447d56ad9e313485","tid":1153300,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T13:54:52.000Z","msg":"專家警告川普對華提高關稅可能引發貿易戰爭<br />\nBINYAMIN APPELBAUM<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2016年5月3日</span></span><br />\n<br />\n在競選活動中，唐納德&middot;J&middot;川普(Donald J. Trump)做出的不少承諾超出了美國總統的權力範圍，比如讓墨西哥出錢在美墨邊境修牆。不過，在對外貿易方面，川普如果真的當上了美國總統，他手中的權力就會和他膨脹的野心更加匹配。<br />\n當上總統，川普就有權力尋求對一些國家施加懲罰，理由是這些國家給美國生產商帶來損失，或者竊取了美國的想法。他還可以向國會尋求立法，比如按照他提出的，對中國的進口商品徵收45%的關稅。<br />\n一些專家表示，關鍵在於，川普可能的確會有擠壓中國的能力。<br />\n但是，這並不意味着他的懲罰措施可以緩解美國的經濟陣痛。事實上，很多專家認為，更大的可能是川普的提議會加劇這些問題，特別是中國或其他被針對的國家也許不僅不接受他的要求，反而會採取報復行動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.nytimes.com/usa/20160503/c03trumptrade/zh-hant/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.nytimes.com%2Fusa%2F20160503%2Fc03trumptrade%2Fzh-hant%2F&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHT0bB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=aa907fff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cn.nytimes.com/usa/20160503/c03trumptrade/zh-hant/</a>"},{"pid":"107d6765faeaf9e5e0d4b55af38ccec9b0b2103d","tid":1153300,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T14:01:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea0affccc3e002d0c9a5ad89a631070a060c4e76","tid":1153300,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T14:18:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9983c338d708a7724c78bcbf7a26e1e948e134d5","tid":1153300,"uid":171446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T14:20:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"368c84283a48e4a3c67746109b1284784c9e4ed4","tid":1153300,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T14:22:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"521ff301d8ddaf7a9bf173d0c06d35773b9c4e0f","tid":1153300,"uid":52595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T14:28:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"22d06e92b1d0029b2510338a39484b92a64e377a","tid":1153300,"uid":14156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T15:35:07.000Z","msg":"加夠200啦 唔好煩"}]}